channel.title: Semi-Old cache stuff
channel.description:
I got on an old computer and I found some odd things.
There's two folders related to runescape .file_store_32 and .jagex_cache_32. Inside both there are runescape and rsmap folders. Here's the contents, just wonder what is useful and what the rsmap is.
.file_store_32
[ul][li]runescape[list] [li]browsercontroll.dll[/li] [li]game_unpacker.dat[/li] [li]jogl.dll[/li] [li]jogl_awt.dll[/li] [li]main_file_cache.dat0 - main_file_cache.dat5 (excluding .dat4) dated from 10/15/08 - 9/6/09[/li] [li]main_file_cache.idx0 - main_file_cache.idx26 dated 9/6/09[/li] [li]main_file_cache.idx255 dated 9/6/09[/li] [/list][/li] [li]rsmap[list] [li]main_file_cache.dat0 dated 7/4/07[/li] [li]main_file_cache.idx0 dated 6/12/07[/li] [/list][/li][/ul]
.jagex_cache_32
[ul][li]runescape[list] [li]jaggl.dll[/li] [li]jagmisc.dll[/li] [li]main_file_cache.dat4 dated 3/19/09[/li] [li]main_file_cache.dat6 dated 3/19/09[/li] [li]main_file_cache.idx27 dated 9/6/09[/li] [li]main_file_cache.idx28 dated 9/6/09[/li] [li]main_file_cache.idx255 dated 9/6/09[/li] [/list][/li] [li]rsmap[list] [li]main_file_cache.dat0 dated 1/22/08[/li] [li]main_file_cache.idx0 dated 1/22/08[/li] [li]main_file_cache.idx1 dated 7/17/07[/li] [/list][/li][/ul]
